@startuml ensure_mqtt_compliance_state

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ReceivePacket : packet received

ReceivePacket --> ParseMQTTPacket

ParseMQTTPacket --> ProtocolError : parsing failed
ParseMQTTPacket --> ValidateMQTTFormat : packet parsed

ValidateMQTTFormat --> ProtocolError : invalid MQTT format
ValidateMQTTFormat --> LogValidationEvent : protocol valid

LogValidationEvent --> Success

Success --> Idle
ProtocolError --> Idle

@enduml